g: </strong>The <a href=\"https://www.rogerslowell.com/news/2021/08/10/member-news/volunteers-help-raise-over-1.36-million-at-2021-will-golf-4-kids-tournament-and-color-of-hope-gala-for-children-s-hospital-northwest/\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">overwhelming generosity</a> of NWA has Arkansas Children's Northwest feeling like they've made a hole in one. The donations will go directly to \"pediatric cancer research and support services.\"</li></ul><p>You can read more about the events and donations <a href=\"https://www.rogerslowell.com/news/2021/08/10/member-news/volunteers-help-raise-over-1.36-million-at-2021-will-golf-4-kids-tournament-and-color-of-hope-gala-for-children-s-hospital-northwest/\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">HERE</a>.</p>"}},"pageContext":{"slug":"do-it-for-the-kids"}},
